title: Wink, Texas
description:
The Seattle Times fired their hockey beat reporter, Marisa Ingemi, who has a history of trashing Barstool Sports & Dave Portnoy (00:01:00). Chris gets real licorice in his Christmas stocking (00:19:00). The hosts of the podcast 'Smartless' really went all out with their Boston live show guest (00:38:35). The Midwest Tour is tossed aside after a caller suggests Wink, Texas... The Home of Roy Orbison (01:56:05). Dave Chappelle threatens to pull his planned projects from his hometown if a new housing plan goes through, a new game from Chris & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
